Welcome to the **go** service agent.

Plain Go service — no gRPC, no REST. Use this for Layer 1 dogfooding: any Go project, build and run with `go build` / `go test`.

## What this agent provides
- Build: `go build`
- Run: run the binary (optional minimal HTTP health)
- Test: `go test ./...`
- Code: LSP (gopls) for ListSymbols

## Production
- Docker build
- Kubernetes deployment (optional)
